OL,5,Cfarming scheme
OL,7,FThe scheme has been put forward by the
OL,8,FWelsh Government to replace EU farming
OL,9,Fsubsidies, which Welsh farmers can no
OL,10,Flonger access after Brexit.
OL,12,FThey are intended to make the industry
OL,13,Fgreener by requiring farmers to plant
OL,14,F10% of their land with trees and using
OL,15,Fanother 10% as a habitat for wildlife.
OL,16,FOnly then would they be eligible for
OL,17,Fthe government payments.
